the lb can be usued as an observation tower for a system observability:
- central place
- trusted component
- already logs

termination codes

lb fairness is something interesting to monitor
higher than average concurrency indicates slow server
low req count indicates slow server

halog can do pretty much everything to check out haproxy logs (grep, percentiles, etc)

tls key generation based on /dev/random instead of /dev/urandom made tls handshake timing out 